Related literature
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Recently, various studies have been done on site specific nutrient management
 recommendations.
 Below, we review some of the most relevant studies.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "beg2024information"
literal "false"

\end_inset

